These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Food: papaya, lemon, spinach
1. Food:lemon is on the right of Food:spinach##1
2. Food:papaya is on the far right##1
3. Food:papaya is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Food   | spinach | lemon | papaya |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Birthday: october, may, july
1. Birthday:may is in an odd position##4
2. Birthday:october is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Birthday   | october | july | may |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Transport: bike, train, quad-bike
1. Transport:train is in an even position##4
2. Transport:train is on the left or right of Transport:quad-bike##3
3. Transport:quad-bike is on the right of Transport:train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Transport   | bike | train | quad-bike |

 #################################
 
